  <Overview>The application polls the Syncthing REST API at regular intervals (default: every 15 minutes) to detect the last modification time of each monitored folder. If a folder has not been modified for longer than a configurable threshold, a notification is sent at the scheduled time.&#13;
&#13;
Supported notification channels:&#13;
- Email (SMTP with STARTTLS or SSL)&#13;
- Gotify (self-hosted push notifications)&#13;
- Discord (webhook</Overview>
